:{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to conjecture, to guess, to presume, to ween, to surmise, to fancy, to assume on ill grounds"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be in a state of fancy, to have illusions, to have exuberant imagination"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to delude, to make believe"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of وَهَمَ (wahama) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"imagination, fancy"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"delusion"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of وَهِمَ (wahima) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/wa.ha.ma/","/wahm/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n44772","headword_ar":"وَهْمٌ","root":"whm","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thought,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an idea, occurring in the mind:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb, * K: *) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awohaAmN","text_ar":"اَوْهَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the two extremes"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"different opinions or ideas"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between which one wavers, that which is outweighed"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in probability"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K.)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"indecisive"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"opinion or idea outweighed in probability"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"or formed from evidence outweighed in probability; a presumption; a surmise; a fancy; a supposition"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: opposed to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zan~N","text_ar":"ظَنٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v. (Kull, p. 376.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Doubt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"suspicion:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but for this I have found no authority; though it is well known, and plainly indicated in the Msb, in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xyl","text_ar":"خيل"},{"kind":"text","text":"; voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xay~ala","text_ar":"خَيَّلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v. in this Lex. ―         -b3-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"object of a thought,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of an idea, occurring in the mind."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.) And The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mind"},{"kind":"text","text":"itself, or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intellect;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaqolN","text_ar":"عَقْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (MF, TA.) In modern Arabic it signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An imagination, a fancy, a chimera,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a conjecture."}],"source_refs":["Msb"]}]}}